SYNOPSIS

    In ~/cpanm-blacklist.conf:

     module=Some::Module
     module=Another::Module
     author=SOMEID

    In the command-line:

     % perl -MModule::Load::In::INIT=App::cpanminus::script::Patch::Blacklist `which cpanm` ...

DESCRIPTION

    This patch adds blacklisting feature to cpanm.

